description:
Autumn is back, and that means a new school year!
How will your uni life look like? What kind of wonderful friends will you meet? Or, perhaps even, what kind of unfortunate people will you be stuck with?
Share your thoughts about this voice pack with the hashtag "#hololiveEN_BackToSchool"!

▶Release Date
On sale from September 2, 2024, 12:00 PM (JST) on the hololive production OFFICIAL SHOP!
